      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <description><![CDATA[<ul><li><strong>Initial release.</strong> Native macOS menubar dictation with Control Option Space, live transcription, clipboard copy, and auto-paste.</li><li><strong>Gravy-ready shipping.</strong> Includes MIT licensing, Sparkle update plumbing, and the download-gated Cloudflare Pages site.</li></ul>]]></description>
